title: Timucuan Ecological & Historic Preserve: Kids & Youth
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Kids & Youth             Kids & Youth          Hey Kids! This page is just for you! Want to explore? Take a walk with a ranger? Look for animals and plants? See a fort? Then you've come to the right place. Check out the links to the left for activities for kids like you. There's activities you can do at the park or from home. And keep an eye out for me - Wade, the Junior Ranger mascot! I'll point out the fun stuff to do online and at the park.        Explore parks with Murray Monster and Elmo. © 2013 Sesame Workshop  Sesame Street has come to the National Parks!  You can watch their adventures, print out a special coloring sheet and even pick up a nature scavenger hunt to use in the Timucuan Preserve.
